Name: Roseau
Description: Roseau is the capital city of Dominica and has many restaurants, small shops and wonderful views of the mountains (to the east) and the Caribbean Sea (to the west).

Name: Portsmouth (Dominica)
Description: Portsmouth is a city in Dominica in the Caribbean.

Name: Scott's Head
Description: Scott's Head is a beautiful village at the end of the road on the southwest corner of Dominica.

Description: Marigot is the largest town and capital of the French side of Saint Martin, an island in the Caribbean.

Name: Morne Trois Pitons National Park
Description: The Morne Trois Pitions National Park is in Dominica. The park is inscribed on the UNESCO World Heritage List.
